name: CheerOutLoud
overview: CheerOutLoud is an online community for people who are passionate about cheerleading. The idea was envisioned by Jason Bass, a visionary in the cheerleading industry. We are a community built for cheerleaders by cheerleaders. We are striving to focus on the best user experience to enable our members to reach out and meet new people around the world as well as improve in the areas of personal development, career development and continuing education in the sport of cheerleading. You’ll find that we aren’t just listing products, companies and competitions; We are offering articles from coaches, videos showing best practices for skills at all levels, a blog to keep you updated on what’s happening around the industry in all corners of the globe and online tools to make staying in touch with your team and coach easier.
